## Clothes's collection For Admin [/admin/collection]

### Add Clothes's Collection[POST]

Admin สามารถเพิ่ม Clothes's Collection ได้

+ Request (application/json)

    + Body
    
            [
            {
                "message": "Add your new cloth's collection in here!",
                
                "detail": [
                    {
                        "name_cloth",
                        "id_cloth",
                        "name_collection",
                        "id_collection",
                        "description_cloth",
                        "cost_cloth",
                        "type_cloth",
                        "material_of_cloth",
                        "sex_cloth",
                        "stock_of_cloth",
                        "date"
                    }
                ]
            }    
            ]
        
+ Response 201 (application/json)


    + Body
    
            [
            {
                "message" :"Your new cloth's collection are complete! 
                            Please check your detail about your new cloth's collection.",
                
                "detail" :
                {
                    "name_cloth":"Hawaii Shirt",
                    "id_cloth":"S_2023_1",
                    "name_collection":"Summer Of 2023",
                    "id_collection":"S_2023",
                    "description_cloth":"This shirt is made to easy to wear in every single days :-)",
                    "cost_cloth":399,
                    "type_cloth":"Tops",
                    "material_of_cloth":"Linin",
                    "sex_cloth":"Unisex",
                    "stock_of_cloth":10,
                    "date" : 2023-03-20
                }
            }
            ]
        
### Delete Clothes's Collection [DELETE]

Admin สามารถลบ Clothes's Collection ได้

+ Request 

    + Header
    
            id_collection : "S_2023"
        
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Header
    
            Location : /admin/colletion/s_2023

    + Body
    
            [
            {
                    "message" :"Delete Clothes's Collection Complete!"
            }
            ]
 
## Edit description and cost For Admin [/admin/cloth]

### Edit Description And Cost Of Clothes [PUT]

Admin สามารถแก้ไขคำอธิบายและราคาของ Clothes's Collection ได้พร้อมลงวันที่การแก้ไขข้อมูลครั้งล่าสุด

+ Request (application/json)

    + Body
    
            
            {
                "data_cloth":{
                    "id_cloth":"Y2K_1"
                },
                
                "detail":{
                    "description_cloth",
                    "cost_cloth",
                    "date" 
                }
            
            }
            
  
+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Header
    
            Location : /admin/cloth/Y2K_1
            

    + Body
    
            [
                {
                "message" :"Your new correction are complete! 
                            Please check your detail about your new correction.",
        
                    "detail": {
                        "description_cloth":"...Description...",
                        "cost_cloth":659,
                        "date":"2023-05-24" 
                    }
                
            }
            ]

