## Basket For User [/user/basket]

### View Orders In User's Basket [GET]

User สามารถดูรายการสั่งซื้อสินค้าในตะกร้าได้

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id_basket" : "basket0001",
                
                "message" :"Your orders are here!",
            
                "detail" : "name_cloth":"Cargo Pant",
                            "id_cloth":"Into_wood_1",
                            "name_collection":"Into the wood",
                            "id_collection":"Into_wood",
                            "description_cloth":"...",
                            "cost_cloth":699,
                            "type_cloth":"Bottoms",
                            "material_of_cloth":"Cotton",
                            "sex_cloth":"Male",
                            "stock_of_cloth":14,
                            "date" : 2023-03-21
            }
        ]

### Add Clothes Into User's Basket [POST]

User เพิ่มเสื้อผ้าที่ต้องการซื้อลงในตะกร้า

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "id_collection": "Y2K",
            "id_cloth": "Y2K_1"
        }
        
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Header
    
            Location : /user/basket/basket0001

    + Body
            
            {
                "message" : "Add cloth to basket are complete !"
            }
            

### Delete Clothes In User's Basket [DELETE]

User ลบเสื้อผ้าที่ไม่ต้องการซื้อออกจากตะกร้า
+ Request

            { 
                "id_basket": "basket0001" 
                "id_cloth" : "Y2K_1"
            }
            
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Header
    
            Location : /user/basket/basket0001/Y2K_1

    + Body
    
            {
                "message" : "Delete cloth in basket are complete !"
            }

  


### Confirm Order In User's Basket [PUT]

User ตกลงสั่งซื้อสินค้าในตะกร้า

+ Request

            { 
                "id_basket": "basket0001" 
            }
        

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "message" :"Your order is done! Thank you. Have a nice day."
            }
        ]